Chordate began to shiver a little harder as Feline pulled him very close, and 
she was now purring which caused her body to give off a soft vibration. 

He moved his hand to the back of her neck, lightly moving it from her neck 
down to her back, kissing her.  He stopped for a moment.  "Uh, how about that 
walk?" he asked, slightly blushing.
